Popular relationship expert and therapist, Blessing Nkiruka aka Blessing CEO has recently taken to Instagram to unveil her pregnancy to her fans and this has sparked enormous reactions on social media.
In the late hours of Valentine’s Day, the mother of one took to her verified Instagram page to share a video of herself as she shows off her pregnancy. Taking to the caption, she said she can’t hide it anymore that the baby is a girl. The relationship expert added that this is one of the reasons why she has been adding weight recently.
“Can’t Hide anymore, she is a girl. Now you know why I have been adding weight” – She wrote

Many of her fans and admirers were surprised at this news. The news came as a shock to many as it was not expected. They took to the comment section to congratulate the relationship expert and also wish her more blessings in the future.
Many top celebrities also commented on the video and congratulated the celebrity. Some of the celebrities that commented include Benson Okonkwo, Chika Lann, and others.
See comments below
Blessing CEO has not revealed the father of the unborn baby to the public.


